<div id="donate-modal" 
     class="modal fade" 
     tabindex="-1" 
     role="dialog">
  <div class="modal-dialog" 
       role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header bg-primary">
        <h4 class="modal-title">Enjoying ManyTwitch?</h4>
        <button type="button" 
                class="close btn btn-primary"
                data-bs-dismiss="modal" 
                aria-label="Close"
                title="Close">
          <span aria-hidden="true">
            <i class="fa fa-close"></i>
          </span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>I built ManyTwitch, because I wanted to be able to watch my favorite creators on Twitch at the same time. If you enjoy using this app, please consider donating a dollar or two to help keep it running. ManyTwitch will always be free, will never feature ads and will never collect information about you or who you watch. Thanks for visiting!</p>
        <p class="text-center strong">Click below to support ManyTwitch!</p>
        <div class="d-grid gap-2">
          <a href="https://ko-fi.com/antillian"
             title="Donate to Antillian! (Opens a new tab)"
             class="btn btn-lg btn-success"
             target="_blank">
             Donate!&nbsp;<i class="fa fa-heart"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>